    "V. EXPERIMENTAL RESULTSThis chapter reports empirical results and analyzes uncertainty estimates across imputation methods.",
    "We first tune key parameters (Section V-A), then summarize runtime (Section V-B) and accuracy (Section V-C), and finally evaluate uncertainty and calibration (Section V-D).",
